   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> La Scultura </s>
            </p>
            <p rend="writing-mode(vertical-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Proprietà artistica riservata - N 1040 </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>La Scultura</head>
               <figDesc> Un bambino scolpisce una statua osservato da una bambina
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Modena, li 6/6-1917.</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p>
                     <lb/>            Forse ti parrà una pasfione morbosa,<lb/>            forse, se gli eventi rimangono avversi <lb/>            parrà diventare.... è già il tormento <lb/>            lo affanno dell'animo e non cesfa<lb/>            e non muore. Ti parrà debolezza di <lb/>            spirito malato, un pensiero forse. persi-<lb/>            stente, indistruttibile, qual'è il mio <lb/>            per te? E come si dovrebbe amare?</p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <s>
                     <lb/>
                     <signed>
                        <persName>
                           <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                        </persName>
                     </signed>
                  </s>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="address-destination">
               <p>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <lb/>            Gent.ma Sig.na <lb/>            Oliva Turtura <lb/>            Via Girolamo Rosfi 58 <lb/>            Ravenna</addrLine>
                  </address>
               </p>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 96 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
